articles.author: Mason Leib
articles.title: Miss USA names new 2023 titleholder after former winner resigned title - Good Morning America
articles.description: The Miss USA pageant has named a successor to the Miss USA title after Noelia Voigt resigned on Monday.
articles.content: The Miss USA pageant named the new 2023 titleholder as Savannah Gankiewicz, Miss Hawaii USA and the first runner-up in the 2023 Miss USA competition on Thursday, according to the pageant's Instagram … [+1856 chars]
